---
title: Mild & Creamy Fish Curry with Toasted Coconut and Rice
description: This curry doesn't bite! Its north Indian spice is tempered by a creamy sauce which goes perfectly with tender fish and flavoursome veggies. Golden toasted coconut emphasises the sweet notes and it's all served with fragrant basmati rice. Nothing to be afraid of!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mild-creamy-fish-curry-c0f94692-8c5d74f3.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/mild-creamy-fish-curry-59022a5bc6243b0a695d9612-d0e332a8.pdf
author: Mimi Morley
